cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.HC 

This paper is about neural machine translation systems and their interaction with human agents. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also discusses online learning techniques, which are commonly used in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also touches on information retrieval (cs.IR) as it discusses the incorporation of new knowledge into the translation system. Finally, the paper discusses the reduction of human effort, which is a topic in human-computer interaction (cs.HC).
